{"word":"H5246 - נָמֵר - nâmêr - naw-mare' - Leopard","slug":"H5246","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָמֵר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nâmêr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-mare'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Leopard"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05DE;&#x05E8; - na&#x0302;me&#x0302;r</b> - <i>naw-mare'</i><p/>From an unused root meaning properly to <i>filtrate</i>, that is, <i>be limpid</i> (compare <a href=\"#/H5247\">H5247</a> and <a href=\"#/H5249\">H5249</a>); and thus to <i>spot</i> or <i>stain</i> as if by dripping; a <i>leopard</i> (from its stripes): - leopard."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5247\">H5247</a>, <a href=\"#/H5248\">H5248</a>, <a href=\"#/H5249\">H5249</a>, <a href=\"#/H5250\">H5250</a>"}]}